  // Validate API keys format
  export const validateApiKeys = (keys: string[]): boolean => {
    const validPattern = /^AIzaSy[A-Za-z0-9_-]{35}$/;
    return keys.every(key => validPattern.test(key));
  };
  
  // Configuration for Gemini API usage
  export const GEMINI_CONFIG = {
    model: 'gemini-2.5-flash-latest',
    baseUrl: 'https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models',
    maxRetries: 3,
    timeoutMs: 30000,
    rateLimitPerMinute: 60, // Free tier limit per key
    rateLimitPerDay: 1500,  // Free tier daily limit per key
    
    // Generation settings optimized for bot detection
    generationConfig: {
      temperature: 0.1,        // Low temperature for consistent analysis
      topK: 1,                 // Focus on most likely tokens
      topP: 0.8,              // Balanced nucleus sampling
      maxOutputTokens: 1024,   // Sufficient for analysis response
      candidateCount: 1        // Single response needed
    }
  };
  
  // Usage tracking interface
  export interface ApiKeyUsage {
    keyIndex: number;
    requestsToday: number;
    requestsThisMinute: number;
    lastRequestTime: Date;
    isBlocked: boolean;
    blockReason?: string;
  }
  
  // Initialize API key manager with your keys
  import { geminiKeyManager } from '../utils/apiKeyManager';
  
  // Call this during app initialization to load your real keys
  export const initializeGeminiKeys = () => {
    // Validate keys before initializing
    if (!validateApiKeys(GEMINI_API_KEYS)) {
      console.warn('Some API keys may be invalid format. Please check your GEMINI_API_KEYS.');
    }
    
    // Update the key manager with real keys
    geminiKeyManager.updateApiKeys(GEMINI_API_KEYS);
    
    console.log(`✅ Initialized ${GEMINI_API_KEYS.length} Gemini API keys for ClippIntell bot detection`);
    console.log(`🔍 Key validation: ${validateApiKeys(GEMINI_API_KEYS) ? 'PASSED' : 'FAILED'}`);
  };
  
  // Export for debugging and monitoring
  export const getApiKeyStats = () => {
    return geminiKeyManager.getDetailedStats();
  };
